<i>♪</i>

1036
00:39:32.695 --> 00:39:34.044
Hey. we get anything from
Aaliyah's SD card?

1037
00:39:34.175 --> 00:39:35.219
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

1038
00:39:35.350 --> 00:39:36.917
It's not pretty.

1039
00:39:37.047 --> 00:39:40.007
<i>- No.
No. please don't do this.</i>

1040
00:39:40.137 --> 00:39:43.053
<i>If you had just
given it to Tengku.</i>

1041
00:39:43.184 --> 00:39:45.534
<i>we wouldn't have to do this.</i>

1042
00:39:45.665 --> 00:39:47.014
<i>[grunts]</i>

1043
00:39:47.144 --> 00:39:48.711
Stop it right there.

1044
00:39:48.842 --> 00:39:50.060
Did he say "Tengku"?

1045
00:39:50.191 --> 00:39:52.454
- Tengku International.
A Malaysian company.

1046
00:39:52.585 --> 00:39:54.804
Maybe you've heard of them
because

1047
00:39:54.935 --> 00:39:58.025
they just secured the city's
very last casino license.

1048
00:39:58.155 --> 00:40:00.201
Davis's replacement
just made the announcement.

1049
00:40:00.331 --> 00:40:01.637
I'm sorry. that's it?

1050
00:40:01.768 --> 00:40:03.247
They wanted their bid
to go through.

1051
00:40:03.378 --> 00:40:04.031
the commissioner
wouldn't give it to them.

1052
00:40:04.161 --> 00:40:05.598
so he had him killed?

1053
00:40:05.728 --> 00:40:07.643
It worked.

1054
00:40:07.774 --> 00:40:10.385
- Well. no. it's not over yet.
We have this footage.

1055
00:40:10.516 --> 00:40:12.561
I'm gonna reach out
to Interpol. LEGAT. CIA.

1056
00:40:12.692 --> 00:40:14.433
and we're gonna put Tengku

1057
00:40:14.563 --> 00:40:17.044
and all their cronies
on the radar.

1058
00:40:17.174 --> 00:40:18.175
I'm not gonna hold my breath

1059
00:40:18.306 --> 00:40:26.306
for someone to make that case.

1060
00:40:28.316 --> 00:40:29.578
A Muslim doctor is murdered.

1061
00:40:29.709 --> 00:40:31.885
We burned ourselves
to an entire community.

1062
00:40:32.015 --> 00:40:33.495
all so that a guy
halfway around the globe

1063
00:40:33.626 --> 00:40:34.931
could get a casino license?

1064
00:40:35.062 --> 00:40:37.064
Wild ride.

1065
00:40:37.194 --> 00:40:39.806
But we did get the guy that
committed the actual murder.

1066
00:40:39.936 --> 00:40:40.894
so it's not nothing.

1067
00:40:41.024 --> 00:40:42.765
[phone chimes]

1068
00:40:42.896 --> 00:40:44.985
6:18. sunset.

1069
00:40:45.115 --> 00:40:46.160
No more shop talk.

1070
00:40:46.290 --> 00:40:47.422
Let's eat.

1071
00:40:47.553 --> 00:40:48.684
Congratulations.

1072
00:40:48.815 --> 00:40:50.120
Thank you.

1073
00:40:50.251 --> 00:40:51.992
Three fasts down.

1074
00:40:52.122 --> 00:40:53.428
27 to go.

1075
00:40:53.559 --> 00:40:55.343
Maybe 26 for me.

1076
00:40:55.474 --> 00:40:56.866
I use moonsighting method.

1077
00:40:56.997 --> 00:40:58.694
See. that's what
I don't understand.

1078
00:40:58.825 --> 00:41:00.696
This is one of the biggest
holidays in the world.

1079
00:41:00.827 --> 00:41:03.394
and we all can't agree on when
it starts or when it ends.

1080
00:41:03.525 --> 00:41:06.136
And that's why we celebrate
Eid twice in my household.

1081
00:41:06.267 --> 00:41:08.704
I think I'm gonna head back
to the mosque. though.

1082
00:41:08.835 --> 00:41:10.010
try and apologize.

1083
00:41:10.140 --> 00:41:11.968
You need backup?

1084
00:41:12.099 --> 00:41:14.275
There's nothing
you need to apologize for?

1085
00:41:14.405 --> 00:41:15.929
Just want to come
for moral support?

1086
00:41:16.059 --> 00:41:17.931
My mother told me.
never apologize

1087
00:41:18.061 --> 00:41:22.326
and never bring your wallet
on a first date.

1088
00:41:22.457 --> 00:41:25.068
It's a first date.

1089
00:41:25.199 --> 00:41:27.244
Technically. we did go
undercover together.

1090
00:41:27.375 --> 00:41:28.550
so it is more like
a second date.

1091
00:41:28.681 --> 00:41:32.336
Ah. second date. OK.

1092
00:41:32.467 --> 00:41:34.295
Actions speak louder than words.

1093
00:41:34.425 --> 00:41:36.079
I think showing up for the Imam.

1094
00:41:36.210 --> 00:41:40.649
he will understand.

1095
00:41:40.780 --> 00:41:44.871
And I'd love to come with you.

1096
00:41:45.001 --> 00:41:46.829
OK. fine.

1097
00:41:46.960 --> 00:41:50.441
You can come with me.

1098
00:41:50.572 --> 00:41:53.053
But first. we need more kibbeh

1099
00:41:53.183 --> 00:41:54.968
and more macarona bechamel.

1100
00:41:55.098 --> 00:41:57.492
Is that so?

1101
00:41:57.623 --> 00:41:59.973
Unless you're in a rush.

1102
00:42:00.103 --> 00:42:02.976
No. no rush.

1103
00:42:03.106 --> 00:42:04.368
OK.

1104
00:42:04.499 --> 00:42:06.980
But technically.

1105
00:42:07.110 --> 00:42:09.939
we've had three dates today.

1106
00:42:10.070 --> 00:42:11.332
This is my fourth.

1107
00:42:11.462 --> 00:42:13.290
[laughs]

1108
00:42:13.421 --> 00:42:14.814
What about a double date?

1109
00:42:14.944 --> 00:42:16.685
- That's bad.
- It's good!

1110
00:42:16.816 --> 00:42:17.817
[laughing] It's really bad.

1111
00:42:17.947 --> 00:42:18.992
It's good.

1112
00:42:19.122 --> 00:42:24.563
<i>♪</i>

1113
00:42:30.046 --> 00:42:32.788
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

1114
00:42:32.919 --> 00:42:40.919
♪

1115
00:42:49.457 --> 00:42:51.024
[wolf howls]
